zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ufm1665703179207.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ufm1665703179207.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ufm1665703179207.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ufm1665703179207\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Encode a null terminated string in Base64 format.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__topic_d132626e1_d132627e1_d132628e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__p_d132629e1_d132630e1_d132631e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">extern long UBase64Enc(const unsigned char *</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">In</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, unsigned char</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">*</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Out</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">, long</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OutMaxLen</var>);</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__section_w4359ab1b5b3_w4360ab1b5_w4361ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d113798e77\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Parameter</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Direction</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">In</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">IN</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">UTF8 string that is to be encoded</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Out</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">OUT</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Base64 encoded result</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">OutMaxLen</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">IN</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15812e1_d15813e1_d15814e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Maximum number of bytes that can be written to <var class=\"keyword varname\">Out</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__section_w4362ab1b5b5_w4363ab1b5_w4364ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d113798e197\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__1\"> Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__2\"> Meaning </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__1\">&lt; 0</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__2\">Not all characters have been\n                    encoded.<p class=\"p\">(<code class=\"ph codeph\">-1</code> x <var class=\"keyword varname\">ReturnValue</var>) have been\n                  encoded.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__1\"> 0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__2\">Failed to encode in base64</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__1\">&gt; 0 </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_d15815e1_d15816e1_d15817e1__entry__2\">All characters have been encoded. The value is the\n                actual length of the output data.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__section_w4365ab1b5b7_w4366ab1b5_w4367ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d113798e264\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__p_d132800e1_d132801e1_d132802e1\">Library <span class=\"ph filepath\">uenc</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__section_w4368ab1b5b9_w4369ab1b5_w4370ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d113798e276\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__p_d132647e1_d132648e1_d132649e1\">This function is useful for creating security drivers\n        that need to encode and decode data.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__section_qjz_jq1_4cc\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_evy_ypg_q3c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Related learning videos</span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Title</th>\n<th class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">link</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__1\">Using $encode to convert to base64 or hex</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\" headers=\"ufm1665703179207__table_evy_ypg_q3c__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"https://vimeo.com/1147368461\" rel=\"external noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img alt=\"Watch or listen using $encode to convert to base64 or hex video\" class=\"image\" id=\"ufm1665703179207__image_nvt_tfg_q3c\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/My_Video_Button.jpg?_LANG=enus\"/></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/arw1665703179582.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>UBase64Dec</a><p>Decode a null terminated Base64 encoded string to string.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532659\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2532659\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "UBase64Enc Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 18, 2026 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Encode a null terminated string in Base64 format. extern long UBase64Enc(const unsigned char * In , unsigned char * Out , long OutMaxLen ); Parameters Parameter Direction Description In IN UTF8 string that is to be encoded Out OUT Base64 encoded result OutMaxLen IN Maximum number of bytes that can be written to Out Return Values Value Meaning < 0 Not all characters have been encoded. ( -1 x ReturnValue ) have been encoded. 0 Failed to encode in base64 > 0 All characters have been encoded. The value is the actual length of the output data. Use Library uenc Description This function is useful for creating security drivers that need to encode and decode data. Table 1. Related learning videos Title link Using $encode to convert to base64 or hex Related Links UBase64Dec Decode a null terminated Base64 encoded string to string. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}